# TASKS

> Your single source of truth for what's active. Read at session start. Update when tasks change.

## Tag legend

- **[ME]** — only you can do this
- **[AGENT]** — Claude executes autonomously
- **[TOGETHER]** — needs your input before Claude can proceed
- **[WIP]** — actively in progress

No tag = treat as [ME].

## Acceptance criteria (AC) on [AGENT] tasks

Every `[AGENT]` task should have a 1–2 line AC field defining what "done" looks like. Claude verifies against it before marking `[x]`.

Bad: `[AGENT] Research buyers for Project X`
Good: `[AGENT] Build buyer long-list for Project X | AC: 15+ names, scored table, outreach draft for top 5`

